sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor A as Admin
  participant UI as UI
  participant K as Kong
  participant PAY as Plan Payment
  participant SQL as SQL

  A->>UI: Edit plan
  UI->>K: PUT /api/v1/admin/plans/id JWT admin role
  K->>PAY: forward
  PAY->>SQL: update plan row
  PAY-->>K: 200
  K-->>UI: updated plan
